Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 你聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近也有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個也是「球棒少年」干的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個是指那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說某個旅館的住客遭到襲擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴨原太太剛搬到這裏 還不太瞭解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 不用太勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C棟鶴田家的兒子患上考試綜合癥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐 竟遇上那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那也是「球棒少年」做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再對任何人提起？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說 不說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小修 夜宵…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要夜宵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的考試很重要 別來煩我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有東西掉了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再堅持一下 一定會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我要離開一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bat(球棒)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先聽說是自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 開始我也不敢相信哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了 說起來我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 關於「球棒少年」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是前陣子的那事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四大街的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 那個媳婦殺害婆婆的案件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害婆婆！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那也是「球棒少年」干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再對任何人提起？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說 不說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管這東西叫魚丸湯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種超市買的廉價貨能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說「不合您的口味嗎」才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂什麼流行不流行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有時間染髮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如多花些時間學學敬語啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這公寓的首期 是誰替你交的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在俊行堅持的份上 才賣了鄉下的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻換來這兔子窩似的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪生不出孩子來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你這死老太婆在才生不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊 你偶爾也該早點回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週三可是我的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要兩個人一起到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小俊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 男人以工作為重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:07:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能總記著什麼生日之類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道總是給你添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做魚丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放三條沙丁魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用研缽搗碎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚要和豆腐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 想造反啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就先還我的首期…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受夠了 我受夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小俊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊 俊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小俊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小俊 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」不是只襲擊精神受壓迫的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是太太被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說是搞錯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為婆婆追了上來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是婆婆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」也不好當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想起了一件搞錯對象的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 是「球棒少年」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再對任何人提起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說 不說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽一個在醫院裏工作的朋友說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井冢太太 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經第三周了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體外受精這麼貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直擔心萬一沒成功的話 不知該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本診所是E.B.M
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是只進行有科學根據的治療
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精子和卵子搞錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精子 川上直人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵子 雛村早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是兩個都弄錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成完全無關的孩子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳出去的話 我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這是頭 這裏是身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經能清晰地看出人形了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很順利吧 我的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺動的很厲害 非常痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊 難道是壓迫性早產
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先檢查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 不會流產吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是你的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 我的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你的寶寶 健康的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 你可愛的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼也不可能有那樣的醫療事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子裏的孩子怎麼可能拿著球棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就有「球棒少年」了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會變成還沒出生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 鴨原太太的丈夫好像是腳本家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳本家？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳本家就是那種的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作就是編故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧 一定好有錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被人稱為「老師」的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太太也應該編些像樣點的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說 我又想起一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹的朋友的表弟的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？「球棒少年」？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再對任何人提起？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說 不說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們初次見面時的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運般的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長一定是神賜予給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當那最後一片枯葉掉落時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶子你一定會好起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人生的最後時刻能與學長一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶子 我不會讓你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不會讓你死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你 如果你不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在了的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎樣活下去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人心酸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過結果兩人如願地一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個故事不會有點怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是有名的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名的什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對對 我想起了關於「有名」的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？是「球棒少年」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天我和丈夫一起看電視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果看見…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九局中已有兩人出局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差最後的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止一直表現很好的投手虻川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內野的選手都圍向了投手板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是第一年 需要這種照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一個了 讓他三振出局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發中間球 開始假裝是直球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後下旋 明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 發外場的低平球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後由我來決定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是內場低球吧 我會飛身撲去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 連外野的選手都跑來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 這會給新人最大的激勵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他打出內場高球 我會接住的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外場高球 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發直球到正中間 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子正在看台上看著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想由我傳出最後的決勝之球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 虻川 按你喜歡的方式投吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 虻川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手虻川會投出什麼樣的球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底投什麼球好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLAY BALL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選手之間的戰術交流不會讓別人聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且真有這事的話 新聞應該會報道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 鴨原太太你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有名的事件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟻冢先生 就是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？誒！那個蟻冢先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 到底發生什麼事會變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THREE！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THREE！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOUR！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 全吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還能不胖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這年頭還要限制飲食 實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」把受食物困擾的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是第100天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經 到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 桅桿？ 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛望鏡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別信口開河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳本家的太太至少也要自重些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 貪污的事敗露了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「球棒少年」叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我豈不是要被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」不是會出現在有麻煩的人身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把「球棒少年」給我叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會有政治家朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢話等睡著了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編也編得像樣點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點真實感都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:20:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是怎樣被打的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣被打的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回答我 到底是怎樣被打的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣被打的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ETC
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間流逝的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安土之王掌管大權
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子招待狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編製著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右都有火之手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著寶物一個勁地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是充滿陰謀的本能寺之變
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.56,0:24:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.52,0:24:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微睡的麻洛美

